    "author": "Beth Sigworth",
    "summary": "With a little experimenting, I came up with these chewy, spicy, oatmeal raisin cookies. They make your kitchen smell wonderful while they are baking. They almost remind me of Christmas because the spices smell so good.",
    "rating": 4.74,
